=== Version 1.0.0

Initial release of yubihsm-manager. Interactive CLI with guided menus for YubiHSM 2 management. Supersedes the previous yubihsm-setup tool with a more user-friendly interface and expanded functionality, including:

Asymmetric key operations: generate, import, sign, decrypt, ECDH derivation, and public key export
X.509 certificate management and attestation certificate signing (device-signed, self-signed, and asymmetric-signed)
Symmetric key operations: generate, import, AES encrypt/decrypt
Wrap key operations: generate, import, export/import wrapped objects
Authentication key management
Device operations: backup, restore, factory reset, and pseudo-random number generation
Guided setup wizards for SunPKCS11 and Microsoft KSP
Scripting: record interactive sessions to JSON script to be executed later for repeatable provisioning
Support for USB and HTTP connections
Cross-platform: Linux (deb/rpm), macOS (Intel and Apple Silicon), and Windows